text: Vyacheslav Poyto (born 11 November 1982) is a Belarusian equestrian. He competed in the individual eventing at the 2008 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1982 births Category:Living people Category:Belarusian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Belarus Category:Equestrians at the 2008 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Minsk
